\par }{\f36\fs20\insrsid15953901\charrsid13586446 "The Cats are ready to go, if that's what you mean, Colonel," Major Megan Powers said, maintaining her slouch. "I've got one full company of armored scouts who know thei
r jobs well enough for me. I could use two more. We've finally got Second Company converted over to all hover tanks. Third is still a hodgepodge of wheels and tracks. But we'll be ready when the balloon goes up."}{
\f36\fs20\insrsid15730155\charrsid13586446 
\par }{\f36\fs20\insrsid15953901\charrsid13586446 Megan pulled herself into a straighter stance. "It}{\i\f36\fs20\insrsid15953901\charrsid12538063  is}{\f36\fs20\insrsid15953901\charrsid13586446 
 about to go, isn't it? That's why you called this meeting, right?"}{\f36\fs20\insrsid15730155\charrsid13586446 
\par }{\f36\fs20\insrsid15953901\charrsid13586446 Lori smiled for the first time in days. If there was one thing that would never change, it was the irascible Megan Powers.}{\f36\fs20\insrsid15730155\charrsid13586446 
