"Dan, I'll be calling pretty heavily on you once we arrive. You've got a more intimate knowledge of the area around the capitol and the Defiance plant than any of us. Consider yourself part of the strategic planning staff on this one."}{
\f36\fs20\insrsid15730155\charrsid13586446 
