\par }{\f36\fs20\insrsid15953901\charrsid13586446 De Argall turned to a thin-faced officer standing at a nearby computer display. "Any idea who they are?"}{\f36\fs20\insrsid15730155\charrsid13586446 
\par }{\f36\fs20\insrsid15953901\charrsid13586446 "Yes, sir," Leutnant-Colonel Don Nix replied, reading from the display. "Radio intercepts suggest that the bogies were 
