-man platoon formed up on the edge of the canyon and, at a signal from their commander, leapt off into the void. Staedler, along with a few members of the }{\i\f36\fs20\insrsid15953901\charrsid12538063 Phobos}{\f36\fs20\insrsid15953901\charrsid13586446 
