\par }{\f36\fs20\insrsid15953901\charrsid13586446 "We are about fifty meters off. From here, it does look like a crashed aerospace fighter." M'Dahlla was silent for a few moments. Then, "It does appear to be a fighter, though it is in bad shape."}{
\f36\fs20\insrsid15730155\charrsid13586446 
