"If it isn't, this is the most through-system traffic I've ever seen at one time," Sellars replied, gesturing toward a holographic representation of the Defiance system. "We first picked up the IR flare here at the nadir point. Then, as the thermal radiat
ion began to fade, we were able to discern at least three starships."}{\f36\fs20\insrsid15730155\charrsid13586446 
\par }{\f36\fs20\insrsid15953901\charrsid13586446 As she spoke, various icons in the holographic display lit up briefly.}{\f36\fs20\insrsid15730155\charrsid13586446 
\par }{\f36\fs20\insrsid15953901\charrsid13586446 "It's really too far to tell, but if I had to guess, I'd say at least one of them is a WarShip."}{\f36\fs20\insrsid15730155\charrsid13586446 
\par }{\f36\fs20\insrsid15953901\charrsid13586446 "WarShips?" Lori's thoughts were brought up by the Warrant Officer's calmly spoken words.}{\f36\fs20\insrsid15730155\charrsid13586446 
\par }{\f36\fs20\insrsid15953901\charrsid13586446 Sellars nodded. "Yes, Colonel, WarShips. When the Separatists rebelled, several ships' crews mutinied, some}{\i\f36\fs20\insrsid15953901\charrsid12538063  en masse.}{\f36\fs20\insrsid15953901\charrsid13586446 
 The Alliance lost at least two Fojr-class corvettes. }{\i\f36\fs20\insrsid15953901\charrsid12538063 And}{\f36\fs20\insrsid15953901\charrsid13586446  there are 
rumors that Victor Davion is lending the rebels aid and technical support. I wouldn't put it past him to be giving them WarShips as well. I've already contacted the}{\i\f36\fs20\insrsid15953901\charrsid12538063  Simon Davion}{
\f36\fs20\insrsid15953901\charrsid13586446  and given her an intercept vector."}{\f36\fs20\insrsid15730155\charrsid13586446 
\par }{\f36\fs20\insrsid15953901\charrsid13586446 "Intercept vector?" Vargas exclaimed. "Are all the ships moving insystem?"}{\f36\fs20\insrsid15730155\charrsid13586446 
\par }{\f36\fs20\insrsid15953901\charrsid13586446 
"Not yet." Sellars pointed to a wedge-shaped scarlet symbol. "But I'm almost certain this is a WarShip of around two hundred fifty thousand tons. That makes it something like a corvette or a destroyer. It could also be a fully loaded}{
\i\f36\fs20\insrsid15953901\charrsid12538063  Monolith}{\f36\fs20\insrsid15953901\charrsid13586446 
 Class JumpShip, but I don't think so. This other one might be another corvette. We just can't get a solid reading on it. Either way, we're in one helluva lot of trouble."}{\f36\fs20\insrsid15730155\charrsid13586446 
