Class."}{\f36\fs20\insrsid15730155\charrsid13586446 
\par }{\f36\fs20\insrsid15953901\charrsid13586446 "Distance to target?" Bern asked.}{\f36\fs20\insrsid15730155\charrsid13586446 
\par }{\f36\fs20\insrsid15953901\charrsid13586446 "Distance to lead target now five hundred kilometers. Distance to trailing target is seven hundred kilometers. Both targets now positively identified as }{\f36\fs20\insrsid15953901\charrsid13721370 Fox}{
