\i\f36\fs20\insrsid15953901\charrsid12538063  Illustrious."}{\f36\fs20\insrsid15730155\charrsid13586446 
\par }{\f36\fs20\insrsid15953901\charrsid13586446 "We
apons officer, prepare a full spread of Killer Whales," Bern ordered. "Get them ready to launch, but do not lock them on target until I give the word. Then I want those missiles out of the tubes in record time."}{
\f36\fs20\insrsid15730155\charrsid13586446 
