tly true, Colonel," Brewer said. "I just did what I thought was best. Then when Colonel McCall relieved me, I went up to the main battle line as he ordered and helped direct our defense. They pushed us a couple of times, but we pushed back. That last time
, I don't think we could have held them if it weren't for Major Goree."}{\f36\fs20\insrsid15730155\charrsid13586446 
