ficers. "You both did a good job out there today, especially you, Captain. And you made the right decision not to pursue the Rangers back to their DropShips. Maybe if the Lyran Guards were here, or if we at least had the full Legion, things might have bee
n different. As it was, getting too close to the DropShips would have been stupid, maybe even suicidal.}{\f36\fs20\insrsid15730155\charrsid13586446 
