w." Goree's tone was as brusque as ever. "Will you salvage your unit and return to Maria's Elegy, or do you intend to stay on here in the Highlands?"}{\f36\fs20\insrsid15730155\charrsid13586446 
\par }{\f36\fs20\insrsid15953901\charrsid13586446 "I've been thinking about that one myself, Major," Lori said. "I don't think we can defend both Maria's Elegy and}{\f36\fs20\insrsid12538063  }{\f36\fs20\insrsid15953901\charrsid13586446 
Defiance. The distance between them is too great. With the maglev out of commission, it just got a little greater. As important as the planetary capital and the spaceport are, the Defiance complex is this planet's primary asset.}{
\f36\fs20\insrsid15730155\charrsid13586446 
\par }{\f36\fs20\insrsid15953901\charrsid13586446 "What I'd like to d
o is recover what 'Mechs I can from the battlefield and from the wreck, move the Legion into the complex, and use it as a base of operations. General Ciampa can either stay in Maria's Elegy or move out here with us. I assume, Major, that your 'Mech facili
ties can handle another regiment or two?"}{\f36\fs20\insrsid15730155\charrsid13586446 
