\f36\fs20\insrsid15953901\charrsid13586446 turned-mercenary. He decided he was too tired to make an issue of Goree's prejudices, and let the matter pass with only an exasperated sigh for a comment.}{\f36\fs20\insrsid15730155\charrsid13586446 
\par }{\f36\fs20\insrsid15953901\charrsid13586446 "Good," Lori continued, ignoring the byplay between the officers. "We'll use the Defiance plant as a base of operations for this area. If the rebels go somewhere else, which I doubt, we'll figure something el
se out."}{\f36\fs20\insrsid15730155\charrsid13586446 
