Over Doctor Sweney's objections, Lori pulled herself to her feet. A sharp lance of pain shot through the 
muscles of her back, and the world side-slipped and took on a reddish hue. She lashed out with her left hand, grabbing McCall by the front of his jumpsuit. The bluff Caledonian stepped forward, catching her under the arms, which set off a new wave of dizz
ying pain.}{\f36\fs20\insrsid15730155\charrsid13586446 
