I'm still alive, you can take me off combat status, but until then, leave me alone."}{\f36\fs20\insrsid15730155\charrsid13586446 
\par }{\f36\fs20\insrsid15953901\charrsid13586446 "Colonel, if you go out to fight, you're going to end up paralyzed, maybe permanently."}{\f36\fs20\insrsid15730155\charrsid13586446 
\par }{\f36\fs20\insrsid15953901\charrsid13586446 "Understood."}{\f36\fs20\insrsid15730155\charrsid13586446 
