\par }{\f36\fs20\insrsid15953901\charrsid13586446 For a second, her anger blazed again. She forced it back down, locking it away in a secure corner of her mind.}{\f36\fs20\insrsid15730155\charrsid13586446 
\par }{\f36\fs20\insrsid15953901\charrsid13586446 "All right, Doctor. I'll wait until the DefHesp pill-pushers have had a chance to poke and prod me."}{\f36\fs20\insrsid15730155\charrsid13586446 
