\par }{\f36\fs20\insrsid15953901\charrsid13586446 "Davis, you and Dan stay here and get the recovery operation going. Have Devin and Houk move their troops over to the Defiance plant. One of Ma
jor Goree's officers will direct them?" The last was more a question aimed at the DSPF commander, who had just returned to the aid station.}{\f36\fs20\insrsid15730155\charrsid13586446 
