\par }{\f36\fs20\insrsid15953901\charrsid13586446 The surest way to reduce the political ramifications of the attack was plain. He had to}{\i\f36\fs20\insrsid15953901\charrsid12538063  win}{\f36\fs20\insrsid15953901\charrsid13586446  the fight for Hesperus.}{
