tening. The pain of losing Davis McCall was still there, along with the overshadowing grief of Grayson's death. However, the fire of determination that had been nearly quenched during the disastrous night attack on the Rangers' bivouac was beginning to bl
aze again.}{\f36\fs20\insrsid15730155\charrsid13586446 
