vehicle through a maze of passages and concourses until she reached what the DSPF referred to as "the officer's block." Lori's temporary quarters and office, along with those assigned to Gina Ciampa, were housed in the same building as Goree's permanent a
ccommodations. She parked the cart in a layby carved out of the living rock of the mountain for just such a purpose, and ducked inside the block.}{\f36\fs20\insrsid15730155\charrsid13586446 
