\par }{\f36\fs20\insrsid15953901\charrsid13586446 The coda to Goree's simple sentence piqued Lori's curiosity, but filled her with apprehension as well. "Reinforcements?" she asked.}{\f36\fs20\insrsid15730155\charrsid13586446 
