\par }{\f36\fs20\insrsid15953901\charrsid13586446 "You said it was a massive intrusion," Lori said. "Do we have any idea how big the incoming force is?"}{\f36\fs20\insrsid15730155\charrsid13586446 
\par }{\f36\fs20\insrsid15953901\charrsid13586446 "I asked them the same thing. All they could say is that it was big. That could mean it was a single big JumpShip or several smaller ones. It could even be another WarShip, for all we know."}{
\f36\fs20\insrsid15730155\charrsid13586446 
\par }{\f36\fs20\insrsid15953901\charrsid13586446 "I doubt it," Lori said.}{\f36\fs20\insrsid15730155\charrsid13586446 
\par }{\f36\fs20\insrsid15953901\charrsid13586446 "Why's that, Colonel?" Goree asked sharply.}{\f36\fs20\insrsid15730155\charrsid13586446 
\par }{\f36\fs20\insrsid15953901\charrsid13586446 
"The rebels already have one WarShip insystem. They haven't really used her since they leveled half the spaceport. Why would they move a second combat ship into Hesperus when they haven't been using the assets they've got?"}{
\f36\fs20\insrsid15730155\charrsid13586446 
