\f36\fs20\insrsid15953901\charrsid13586446 Archon to send in a relief force to break up the invasion and secure Hesperus II for the Alliance. In that case, they might send another WarShip to try to stop the relief force.}{
\f36\fs20\insrsid15730155\charrsid13586446 
