 That was right before they started bombarding the spaceport. As for the other ship, we're reasonably certain it went to meet the other Ranger JumpShips and that one of those jumped out}{\f36\fs20\insrsid7091749 -}{
\f36\fs20\insrsid15953901\charrsid13586446 system. Why do that? The only reason I can think of is to call for reinforcements."}{\f36\fs20\insrsid15730155\charrsid13586446 
