heir side, wholesale, or if Kelswa and Dundee manage to scrape together enough money to hire a mercenary outfit or two, what we see on Hesperus right now is what they've got."}{\f36\fs20\insrsid15730155\charrsid13586446 
\par }{\f36\fs20\insrsid15953901\charrsid13586446 "So, what we've got inbound then is the Seventeenth Rangers?" Lori asked.}{\f36\fs20\insrsid15730155\charrsid13586446 
