\par }{\f36\fs20\insrsid15953901\charrsid13586446 "If that's the case, we're in deep trouble," Ciampa said. "We can recall the Thirty-sixth Guards from Maldon, but given our losses, that will only put us at, what, six full 'Mech battalions, if
