\par }{\f36\fs20\insrsid15953901\charrsid13586446 "Not yet." Goree shrugged, shaking his head. "They've been observing strict radio silence ever since they entered Hesperus orbit. Unless Colonel Kalmar-Carly
le wants to launch a fighter to go take a look, we're going to have to wait until these ships are on the ground to find out who they are."}{\f36\fs20\insrsid15730155\charrsid13586446 
